{"tid":2045452,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"Twitter戰線: 無視極左 駁斥5毛 齊反警暴","createTime":"2020-05-31T22:51:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-01T02:44:44.000Z","uid":293844,"like":17,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"cc04d929f2a3a3634178f73a850b6a7b0ab9daa6","tid":2045452,"uid":293844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T22:51:32.000Z","msg":"睇左成日Twitter / Reddit, 有少少意見分享下<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">1. 無視Antifa等極左白人團體同支持者</span></span><br />\nAntifa其實只有少數美國人支持，佢地跟本想騎劫成個#BlackLivesMatter 運動。 呢班人好多都唔係黑人或少數族裔，只係中二病搞無政府主義。無謂晒時間同佢地泥漿摔角。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">2. 駁斥5毛、小粉紅散播有關香港嘅fake news</span></span><br />\n5毛同小粉紅不斷扮香港人抵毀、抹黑香港抗爭。大家有必要正視聽，講返香港人自發搞抗爭、追求民主自由、對抗共產(真法西斯)極權。我地抗爭唔關共和黨、CIA事。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">3. Connect美國大眾，講返香港人都係反黑警</span></span><br />\n由於歐美政壇都比較多左翼，所以要預左好多美國人係左膠同反Trump，同埋佢地好多人根本就唔知(同唔信)Trump咁撐香港民主自由。如果有手足好反感，可以無視呢點，但係求求各位唔好因為人地唔支持Trump就屌。由於Trump唔係習維尼，無得做成世，我地唔應該將所有希望押落Trump度，要connect埋普通美國人。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">我地唔洗話自己反Trump，只要講返香港人都係警暴受害者，同情、理解佢地就OK。</span> 歐洲嗰邊已經有集會撐美國示威，香港人唔應該miss左connect西方自由世界嘅機會。<br />\n<br />\n國際戰線冇得放棄，有時難免要策略啲諗，避重就輕，為香港抗爭爭取最大利益。各位手足繼續努力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e00e5c120459728847ff35a064968be1cca3d73","tid":2045452,"uid":293844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T22:55:16.000Z","msg":"空氣Push"},{"pid":"55bb7e9fb1b1c01e021316b19dbbc3b3c50c5651","tid":2045452,"uid":67553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T22:56:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd7ca992f731fea4f0338b093ac17d2843f48761","tid":2045452,"uid":333002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T23:04:39.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"3904bee145989fe6dfc45207f6be3d9e70371e56","tid":2045452,"uid":108359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T23:13:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5499dea7c3c46350c81e3e11ee120570dd8022d7","tid":2045452,"uid":154486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T23:21:33.000Z","msg":"push<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/29NqdBL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F29NqdBL.jpg&h=2f4e62f2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"59a8b1f16365ba3b773bbe4338889fb902773d9f","tid":2045452,"uid":187755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T23:57:35.000Z","msg":"支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n[國際線要人]BBC證實大量小粉紅在Facebook, Twitter, YouTube攻擊香港和美國<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2044782\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2044782</a>"},{"pid":"f577e4de6b863d018af21b84b87e4b870a9e8491","tid":2045452,"uid":340040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T00:01:31.000Z","msg":"Agger"},{"pid":"3ea3cb3938baf6e7fe33605b687974cb17340194","tid":2045452,"uid":85751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T00:22:59.000Z","msg":"#StandUp4humanrights <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddfaff663ea611c86997d10ef06181e79a5cc600","tid":2045452,"uid":234089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T00:24:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d018d9fa0869d774632368062f1c3a2181c4c283","tid":2045452,"uid":191588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T00:27:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e07e59dbcbe5844b29a44f3f248221d9159afd39